    <item>
      <title>马克·库班在 2024 年支持拜登，敦促在药品成本方面采取更多行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/mark-cuban-backs-biden-over-trump-in-2024-calls-for-drug-cost-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·库班敦促总统乔·拜登进一步控制处方药成本，这是他连任竞选的一个关键因素，因为他在 11 月可能与唐纳德·特朗普复赛之前支持现任总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/mark-cuban-backs-biden-over-trump-in-2024-calls-for-drug-cost-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:22:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院被要求阻止德克萨斯州移民驱逐法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/supreme-court-asked-to-block-law-letting-texas-deport-migrants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府要求美国最高法院阻止德克萨斯州一项允许该州逮捕并驱逐非法入境者的法律，这为法院的选举年日历增添了又一​​个带有政治色彩的案件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/supreme-court-asked-to-block-law-letting-texas-deport-migrants</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:12:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾寻求企业资助 430 亿美元的项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/asia-s-growth-star-woos-companies-for-projects-worth-43-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾正在重新推动企业为从机场到公交专用道等基础设施提供资金，目前价值 430 亿美元，旨在在财政空间有限的情况下保持其作为亚洲增长明星之一的光彩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/asia-s-growth-star-woos-companies-for-projects-worth-43-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国资助协议对司法部对苹果、Ticketmaster 的反垄断调查造成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/us-funding-deal-delivers-blow-to-doj-antitrust-probes-of-apple-ticketmaster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项让联邦政府在 9 月份保持运转的支出协议将限制反垄断执法机构可获得的资金，这可能会阻碍对苹果公司和 Live Nation Entertainment Inc. 旗下 Ticketmaster 的高调调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/us-funding-deal-delivers-blow-to-doj-antitrust-probes-of-apple-ticketmaster</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:31:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉提议为巴西优步司机提供更强有力的劳动保护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/brazil-s-lula-to-propose-stronger-labor-protections-for-uber-drivers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦正在推动加强优步科技公司和类似客运应用程序司机的劳工权利，应对困扰世界各地立法者的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/brazil-s-lula-to-propose-stronger-labor-protections-for-uber-drivers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 15:07:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>海地暴力越狱引发谋杀和骚乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/prison-break-after-violent-gang-raid-sparks-emergency-in-haiti</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周末，全副武装的团伙袭击了该国两座最大的监狱，暴力事件席卷了首都，海地宣布进入紧急状态，并实施夜间宵禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/prison-break-after-violent-gang-raid-sparks-emergency-in-haiti</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 15:03:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚将为东南亚提供十年签证和融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/australia-pledges-1-3-billion-to-spur-southeast-asia-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理安东尼·艾博内塞将推出更长的商务签证和一项 20 亿澳元（合 13 亿美元）的融资安排，作为推动澳大利亚在东南亚贸易和投资的一揽子计划的核心内容，在中美经济存在不确定性的情况下深化区域关系关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/australia-pledges-1-3-billion-to-spur-southeast-asia-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
